products.title: Misguided
products.description: In Tokyo's bustling streets, amidst the vibrant culture, you'll find a breathtakingly beautiful girl, a captivating blend of tradition and modernity. With graceful elegance, she glides through the city's neon-lit nights, her radiant smile illuminating the hearts of those she encounters. Embodying the essence of Japan's timeless charm, this Tokyo belle is a living canvas of artistic allure, leaving an indelible impression on all who cross her path. She embodies the spirit of Tokyo, a city that celebrates beauty in all its diverse forms.

products.title: Toyota soarer
products.description: What Toyota is good for drifting? The Toyota Cresta JZX100 had a well-balanced RWD chassis with a long wheelbase making it easy for the driver to throw the rear around. It used the 1JZ-GTE 2.5-Liter turbocharged engine seen on Soarer and Chaser above on this list. The combination of these factors made it a no-brainer for drifting.
